Description: bc-* ecosystem Hash-Routed Binary Layout (development files)
 Zero-copy mmap reader, parallel writer, verifier and one-way
 JSON / YAML / INI exporters for the `.hrbl` binary format.
 Strict little-endian layout, 8-byte aligned, root index and block
 entries sorted by xxh3_64 with unique keys per scope, integrity
 protected by header + footer xxh3_64 checksums. JSON bootstrap
 convert (JSON → .hrbl) powered by json-c.
 .
 This package ships the static library, public headers, and
 pkg-config descriptor required to build against bc-hrbl.
